WEBVTT

00:01:29.824 --> 00:01:30.547
čarobnjak,

00:01:30.547 --> 00:01:31.261
čarobni štapić,

00:01:31.261 --> 00:01:33.262
i "Wingardium Leviosa",

00:01:33.262 --> 00:01:36.014
sila teže prestala je postojati

00:01:36.014 --> 00:01:37.313
na bilijunima stranica

00:01:37.313 --> 00:01:39.739
koje počivaju na tim policama.

00:01:40.536 --> 00:01:42.684
Autori znanstvene fantastike i fantazije

00:01:42.684 --> 00:01:44.677
doslovno grade svjetove.

00:01:44.677 --> 00:01:45.793
Stvaraju pravila,

00:01:45.793 --> 00:01:46.499
karte,

00:01:46.499 --> 00:01:47.335
loze,

00:01:47.335 --> 00:01:48.186
jezike,

00:01:48.186 --> 00:01:49.085
kulture,

00:01:49.085 --> 00:01:50.470
svemire,

00:01:50.470 --> 00:01:53.056
opcijske svemire unutar svemira,

00:01:53.056 --> 00:01:54.572
i iz tih svijetova niču

00:01:54.572 --> 00:01:56.708
priča, za pričom, za pričom.

00:01:57.058 --> 00:01:58.109
Kada se to radi dobro,

00:01:58.109 --> 00:01:59.411
čitatelji mogu razumjeti

00:01:59.411 --> 00:02:01.589
fikcijske svjetove i njihova pravila